=== Spec Example 6.8. Flow Folding
from: http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2779950
tags: spec whitespace scalar upto-1.2

+++ in-yaml
"
  foo<SPC>
<SPC>
  <TAB> bar

  baz
"

+++ in-json
" foo\nbar\nbaz "

+++ out-yaml
" foo\nbar\nbaz "

+++ test-event
+STR
+DOC
=VAL " foo\nbar\nbaz<SPC>
-DOC
-STR
